To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, this license grants rights similar in spirit to permissive open-source licenses, while preserving truthful representation requirements for the SLANG-Audit name and reference implementation.

If any provision is found unenforceable, the remaining provisions remain in effect.

Nature of Release

This is a minimal reference implementation.

It is intended to demonstrate a structural correctness model—not to represent a complete audit system or regulatory framework.

Behavioral guarantees apply only within the scope of the reference model.

