Closing Statement

SLANG-Audit explores a simple but fundamental idea:

Audit correctness can emerge deterministically from structure, without verification workflows, replay, or reconciliation.

It is released openly to encourage:

independent validation
real-world testing
safe experimentation

SLANG-Audit is offered as a minimal reference implementation of that possibility.
